{"TopicId":170993,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"Terrain Scatter - Enhanced Edition","CreatedByName":"PilotNaut","CreatedById":134388,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-17T00:32:56Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"PilotNaut","CreatedById":134388,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-17T00:32:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know the terrain scatter has been a beta feature for some time, and I apologise if this has been asked before but are there\u003Cbr\u003E\nany plans to bring a basic terrain scatter to the consoles, I feel the planets are just that little bit more interesting with them, helps differentiate hills and stuff, distance...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ZooNamedGames","CreatedById":103726,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-17T14:15:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI couldn\u0027t imagine why this wasn\u0027t included by default. They don\u0027t seem to impact performance all that much from my POV (and I run on hardware that is technically \u003Cem\u003Einferior \u003C/em\u003Eto the consoles) and provide very key distance perception.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt would be like playing the game without shadows. Landing on planets would be a nightmare... especially without mod readouts.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klgraham1013","CreatedById":105132,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-17T18:15:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223297066\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022170993\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221518827576\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022134388\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022PilotNaut\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 hours ago, PilotNaut said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nbeta feature\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDon\u0027t be silly.\u00A0 Released products don\u0027t have beta features.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spartwo","CreatedById":58131,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-02-17T21:36:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223297560\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022170993\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221518891352\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022105132\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022klgraham1013\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, klgraham1013 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDon\u0027t be silly.\u00A0 Released products don\u0027t have beta features.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nlol. Good one.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}